This year French Quarter Festivals, Inc. celebrates its 40th anniversary. FQFI values the unique and creative traditions of our community and strives to celebrate a collection of musical, culinary, and artistic talent that both honors the rich cultural history of our region and welcomes ongoing innovation. 

I serve on the board of FQFI in order to support the continuation of this legacy for many years to come, but we need everyone’s help to make that possible! Join our #GiveNOLADay campaign today and help turn 40 into Forever with a donation today: https://www.givenola.org/frenchquarterfestivalsinc
